hh3cLBv2.name: hh3cLBv2

revisions.description: Initial revision of this MIB module.

hh3cLBv2.contactinfo: Platform Team Hangzhou H3C Tech. Co., Ltd. Hai-Dian District Beijing P.R. China http://www.h3c.com Zip:100085
hh3cLBv2.description: The private MIB file includes the LB information of the device.

hh3cLBv2TrapEnable.name: hh3cLBv2TrapEnable
hh3cLBv2TrapEnable.description: Indicates whether the module of LB will generate traps for events defined in this MIB. 'enabled' results in SNMP traps; 'disabled', no traps are sent.
